{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Limoria</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A single-player psychological horror game. In this experience set in an old and mysterious hotel, you explore constantly shifting spaces that challenge the limits of your mind. Each time you wake up, the hotel and its surroundings change, confronting you with disturbing and strange occurrences. As the player, you gather clues within the depths of the atmosphere and try to understand the mystery behind the crumbling reality.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Explore Your Surroundings</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This psychological horror is filled with elements that cloud your vision with each discovery. The game doesn\u2019t hand you the story directly; to understand it, you must immerse yourself in the atmosphere and pay attention to clues.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3351140/extras/ipucu.gif?t=1735680916\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Find Your Way Out of a Fractured Mind</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">With each level, the protagonist\u2019s mind will deteriorate further. Discover the exit and witness even more mysteries in the process.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3351140/extras/ka\u00e7\u0131\u015f.gif?t=1735680916\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>You Can Escape Anything but Not Your Memories</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Throughout the game, your memories will follow you; even if you\u2019d rather not see them, you\u2019ll pay the price of their consequences.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3351140/extras/\u00e7er\u00e7eve_bak.gif?t=1735680916\" /></p><p c